description.displayText: Francine has been with us for 5 months and I would highly recommend her. She helps to take care of our 3 year old and 9 month old daily. She is creative, adaptable and flexible with our schedules. She has helped with the babies routine and also works in our toddlers patience and focus. She's extremely reliable and we'd recommend her in a heartbeat!

description.displayText: Fran was our Au Pair for two years. She cared for our daughter from the age of 9 months to almost 3 years old. She became like family to our little girl, who thrived under her care. What's distinct about Fran is her connection to the children she cares for-she engages with them each moment of the day. She understands them and connects with them, and is therefore able to bond with them deeply and care for them expertly. Fran is not only incredible with children, but she is also reliable, professional and kind. I highly recommend Fran!

description.displayText: Francine will take your breath away as she not only helps your little one meets their milestones, but she provides meal planning to help meet nutritional needs! We didn't know we needed Fran in our lives till we met her!!! I wish we were still in the East Coast to have Fran continue her magic touch and bring countless smiles to our little girl now a toddler. Fran is an exceptional Nanny, cook, friend, and will become an honorary member to your family as she was/is to ours! We joke that once you have Fran in your life, you will never look for another Nanny as they will have to hold a candle to Fran!
